<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uz">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Studix – Kirish ma'lumotlari</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#0a0a0f;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;">

  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#0a0a0f;min-height:100vh;padding:40px 16px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="560" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width:560px;width:100%;">

          <tr>
            <td style="padding-bottom:32px;text-align:center;">
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="display:inline-table;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6ee7f7,#a78bfa);border-radius:14px;padding:10px 18px;">
                    <span style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#0a0a0f;letter-spacing:-0.5px;">Studix</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

         
          <tr>
            <td style="background:#13131a;border-radius:24px;border:1px solid #1e1e2e;overflow:hidden;">

              
              <tr>
                <td style="height:4px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#6ee7f7,#a78bfa,#f472b6);"></td>
              </tr>

            
              <tr>
                <td style="padding:48px 48px 40px;">

                
                  <div style="width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:16px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(110,231,247,0.15),rgba(167,139,250,0.15));border:1px solid rgba(110,231,247,0.2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:28px;">
                    <span style="font-size:26px;line-height:56px;display:block;text-align:center;">🎓</span>
                  </div>

             
                  <h1 style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#f0f0ff;margin:0 0 8px;letter-spacing:-0.5px;">
                    Xush kelibsiz, {{fullName}}!
                  </h1>
                  <p style="font-size:15px;color:#6b7280;margin:0 0 36px;line-height:1.6;">
                    Studix platformasiga muvaffaqiyatli ro'yxatdan o'tdingiz. Quyida tizimga kirish uchun shaxsiy ma'lumotlaringiz.
                  </p>

           
                  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#0d0d14;border-radius:16px;border:1px solid #1e1e2e;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:32px;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:20px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid #1e1e2e;">
                        <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:#6ee7f7;letter-spacing:1.2px;text-transform:uppercase;">Login (Email)</p>
                        <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;color:#e2e2f0;font-weight:400;">{{email}}</p>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:20px 24px;">
                        <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:#a78bfa;letter-spacing:1.2px;text-transform:uppercase;">Vaqtinchalik parol</p>
                        <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Courier New',monospace;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#f0f0ff;letter-spacing:2px;">{{password}}</p>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                
                  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:rgba(244,114,182,0.08);border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(244,114,182,0.2);margin-bottom:36px;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:16px 20px;">
                        <p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#f472b6;line-height:1.6;">
                          ⚠️ &nbsp;Xavfsizlik uchun tizimga kirganingizdan so'ng parolni darhol o'zgartiring. Parolingizni hech kimga bermang.
                        </p>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

               
                  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6ee7f7,#a78bfa);border-radius:12px;padding:1px;">
                        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                          <tr>
                            <td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6ee7f7,#a78bfa);border-radius:11px;padding:14px 32px;">
                              <a href="#" style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0a0a0f;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:-0.2px;">
                                Tizimga kirish →
                              </a>
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                        </table>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                </td>
              </tr>

            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="padding:28px 0 0;text-align:center;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-size:12px;color:#374151;">
                Bu xat <strong style="color:#6ee7f7;">Studix</strong> tizimi tomonidan avtomatik yuborildi.
              </p>
              <p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#374151;">
                © 2025 Studix. Barcha huquqlar himoyalangan.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

</body>
</html>
